{"tid":1732142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"攻大學係黑9對付黎明嘅策略","createTime":"2019-11-17T23:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T07:37:41.000Z","uid":32511,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a82268d47749f321f719438788168f34e2adbca7","tid":1732142,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:38:02.000Z","msg":"集中我地係一點，等開唔到花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc14da824d55478b3ab432bc80def32445a7963d","tid":1732142,"uid":32511,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"大家仲係唔明，唔係所有大學都要守，有d要守因為地形適合，有d適合做出擊基地，例如理大，人地硬攻對我地好不利。而且仲集中一點方便對家一網打盡。<br />\n<br />\n只有開花先係上策，先可以令敵人頂唔順。見到尋晚到今朝錯誤嘅策略令咁多手足受傷，大家有冇真係反省過？重複犯相同錯誤！<br />\n<br />\n只有繼續開花，干擾交通線，先係上策。而攻打支聯辦先係可以幫理大解圍。"},{"pid":"820fce76eeff6801ebfaa04cbe8a3621148b51b9","tid":1732142,"uid":52939,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:15:15.000Z","msg":"今日交通真係牌撚晒 唉屌"},{"pid":"b4b352db6beb0930711b82f64612537336f2f88d","tid":1732142,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"820fce76eeff6801ebfaa04cbe8a3621148b51b9","tid":1732142,"uid":52939,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:15:15.000Z","msg":"今日交通真係牌撚晒 唉屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:15:28.000Z","msg":"順"},{"pid":"8c43c4a9fbf36b32ff372a5587d324e2f02d3bb7","tid":1732142,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T01:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4707546c0b06fd0b225e3145cc2d8438f0be54c","tid":1732142,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT